show.description: "A girl from a village who just came to be a substitute bride, but with every step she takes, secrets begin to unravel—secrets powerful enough to change everyone’s lives. In this game of love, betrayal, and politics, who is the real bride, and who will emerge victorious? Watch now this gripping tale where behind every secret lies an even bigger twist."
